  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "VvVYqkkEJxVOykf+/oAykYwpFXmP/BVqt2Z8E4i5Diw=",
    "originContent": "- Designed for performance and highly optimized. See the [Benchmarks](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/benchmarks/).",
    "translatedContent": "- 设计注重性能且高度优化。详见[基准测试](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/benchmarks/)。"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "jwuZM87kx7FUNCd9WapwPIvhZLQuAJmmkL2noXcJZYI=",
    "originContent": "- Well-documented, type-safe [API](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/mlange-42/ark), and a comprehensive [User guide](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/).",
    "translatedContent": "- 文档完善，类型安全的[API](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/mlange-42/ark)，以及全面的[用户指南](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/)。"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "kDFmrcK+0hNBeE3IdZPKF3Z01T/MnAK9v2tnKp800kY=",
    "originContent": "- [Entity relationships](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/relations/) as a first-class feature.",
    "translatedContent": "- 将[实体关系](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/relations/)作为一等公民特性。"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "xOYSC19qHWJ+RMRSYYznT3dWco15aHeGptqQZeKvrok=",
    "originContent": "- Extensible [event system](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/events/) with filtering and custom event types.",
    "translatedContent": "- 可扩展的[事件系统](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/events/)，支持过滤和自定义事件类型。"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "3JDHifRmnQcwmhFMwnomI+haAVbcT0f+ac4I0RuvqLY=",
    "originContent": "- Fast [batch operations](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/batch/) for mass manipulation.",
    "translatedContent": "- 快速的[批量操作](https://mlange-42.github.io/ark/batch/)，用于大规模操作。"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "p+gyh1In0OCIQ6OlsOLm+bVkoDL21nWiXG8QfZ+NsOY=",
    "originContent": "- No systems. Just queries. Use your own structure (or the [Tools](https://github.com/mlange-42/ark#tools)).",
    "translatedContent": "- 无系统概念。仅使用查询。使用你自己的结构（或[工具](https://github.com/mlange-42/ark#tools)）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "HwsoTMX9DEwJLQDCkPt1XGUDAXSgWsGsYoMjg1E95s8=",
    "originContent": "- World serialization and deserialization with [ark-serde](https://github.com/mlange-42/ark-serde).",
    "translatedContent": "- 支持通过 [ark-serde](https://github.com/mlange-42/ark-serde) 进行世界的序列化与反序列化。"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "qrThR3Aw183cA4Fw/HBPaO1KxPsxOjtpx5UUMzX9myI=",
    "originContent": "- Zero [dependencies](https://github.com/mlange-42/ark/blob/main/go.mod), 100% [test coverage](https://app.codecov.io/github/mlange-42/ark).",
    "translatedContent": "- 零[依赖](https://github.com/mlange-42/ark/blob/main/go.mod)，100%[测试覆盖率](https://app.codecov.io/github/mlange-42/ark)。"
  },
